rements state error is returned\n122:  # RD-016\n125:    When the user runs \"requirements draft --idea 'Simple change'\"\n131:  # RD-017\n133:    Given a requirements review payload with \"conditionally_approved\" outcome\n135:    When the payload is validated through the requirements_review contract\n139:  # RD-018\n141:    Given a requirements run in \"awaiting_answers\" status\n143:    When the user runs \"requirements answer <run-id>\"\n144:    Then an invalid requirements state error is returned\n147:  # RD-019\n150:    When the user runs \"requirements quick --idea 'Build a REST API'\"\n155:  # RD-020\n158:    When the user runs \"requirements draft --idea 'Simple change'\"\n164:  # RD-021\n166:    Given a requirements run in \"failed\" status at the committed question boundary\n168:    When the user runs \"requirements show <run-id>\"\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
